        "culturalTip": "이 표현은 공손하게 희망을 표현하는 방법이에요!",
        "explanationEn": "This is a grammar used to express wishes or hopes.",
        "whenToUseEn": "\"When Speaking of Hopes\"",
        "culturalTipEn": "This expression is a way to politely express hope!"
