        "culturalTip": "'-고 싶다'는 자신의 희망을 표현할 때만 사용해요!",
        "explanationEn": "\"It's the most direct way to express what you want to do.\"",
        "whenToUseEn": "\"When expressing desires or wishes\"",
        "culturalTipEn": "The phrase '-고 싶다' is only used to express one's own wishes!"
      }
    },
    {
      "stepNumber": 4,
      "type": "single_expression",
      "expression": {
