        "culturalTip": "'원하다'는 명사와 함께, '고 싶다'는 동사와 함께 사용해요.",
        "explanationEn": "This is a verb that expresses what you want. It has a stronger feeling than '고 싶다' (which means 'to want to').",
        "whenToUseEn": "When expressing strong desires",
        "culturalTipEn": "The verb '원하다' (to want) is used with nouns, while '고 싶다' (to want to) is used with verbs."
